                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350202-524-offence-1 t18350202-cd-52"></join>8th of January</rs>, 1 coat, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18350202-name-380" type="victimName">
